# Cozycabin Affiliate Portal Enhancement Pack

This pack is designed to be **additive only** and not replace existing
functionality.

## Add New Firestore Collections

-   affiliateRanks
-   affiliateLeaderboard
-   affiliateNotifications
-   affiliateReferrals
-   affiliateAnalytics

## New Dashboard Sections

### 1. Affiliate Rank Card

``` html
<div id="affiliate-rank-card"></div>
```

Fields: - Current Rank - Sales Progress - Progress Bar - Next Rank

### 2. Earnings Analytics

``` html
<div id="earnings-analytics-card"></div>
```

Show: - Today - Week - Month - Lifetime

### 3. Leaderboard

``` html
<div id="leaderboard-section"></div>
```

Top 10 affiliates by sales.

### 4. Affiliate Academy

Accordion sections: - WhatsApp Selling - Facebook Marketing - TikTok
Marketing - Product Photography - Trust Building

### 5. Referral Program

``` html
<div id="affiliate-referral-section"></div>
```

Show: - Referral Link - Referral Count - Referral Earnings

### 6. Notification Center

``` html
<div id="affiliate-notifications"></div>
```

### 7. Conversion Analytics

``` html
<div id="conversion-analytics"></div>
```

Metrics: - Clicks - Product Views - WhatsApp Opens - Sales - Conversion
Rate

